altername_name: Star Wars Rogue Squadron III: Rebel Strike (Limited Edition Preview Disc)
name: Star Wars: Rogue Squadron III: Rebel Strike Limited Edition Preview Disc
overview: Star Wars Rebel Strike: Rogue Squadron III Limited Edition Preview Disc was acquired via preordering the Star Wars Rebel Strike: Rogue Squadron III and did not see its own release. This disc came in its own case and contained the Atari (1982) Star Wars game, a demo for Rebel Strike, as well as game trailers, and concept art.
